<i>noun</i>: 혜성 [혜ː성/헤ː성] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>혜성 [혜ː성/헤ː성]</dt><br>
<dd>1. comet</dd><br>
<dd>태양을 중심으로 타원이나 포물선을 그리며 도는, 꼬리가 달린 천체.</dd><br>
<dd>A celestial body with a tail, which revolves around the sun in an elliptical or parabolic orbit.</dd><br>
<dd>2. meteor; comet</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 어떤 분야에 갑자기 나타난 매우 뛰어난 존재.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A person who has a meteoric rise to fame in a certain field.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>